    <summary>The Web Security Context Working Group has published a W3C Recommendation of Web Security Context: User Interface Guidelines. This specification deals with the trust decisions that users must make online, and with ways to support them in making safe and...</summary>
    <author>
        <name>W3C Staff</name>
    </author>
    
        <category term="Browsers and Authoring Tools" scheme="http://www.sixapart.com/ns/types#category" />
    
        <category term="Home Page Stories" scheme="http://www.sixapart.com/ns/types#category" />
    
