    <content type="html" xml:lang="en" xml:base="http://www.w3.org/">
        
        <![CDATA[<p>The <a href="/2006/WSC/">Web Security Context Working Group</a> has published  a W3C Recommendation of <a href="/TR/2010/REC-wsc-ui-20100812/">Web Security Context: User Interface Guidelines</a>. This specification deals with the trust decisions that users must make online, and with ways to support them in making safe and informed decisions where possible. It describes user interactions and user interface guidelines with a goal toward making security usable, based on known best practice in this area. 
 Learn more about the <a href="/Security/">Security Activity</a>.</p>]]>
